		"description": {
			"value": "<p>When you cast a @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-rules.JournalEntry.vaLYevRxKe8mAvdE.JournalEntryPage.MNWLud81msaiZukw]{wizard spell} that deals damage using a spell slot of up to 5th level, you can deal maximum damage with that spell.</p><p>The first time you do so, you suffer no adverse effect. <strong>If you use this feature again before you finish a long rest</strong>, you take [[/damage 2d12]] damage for each level of the spell immediately after you cast it. Each time you use this feature again before finishing a long rest, the damage per spell level increases by [[/damage 1d12]]. This damage cannot be reduced or avoided.</p>",
